item.title: Aspose.Email for Python via .NET 23.12 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes information for Aspose.Email for Python via .NET 23.12. Aspose.Email for Python via .NET 23.12 is based on Aspose.Email for .NET 23.12. Features not implemented The following features are not implemented in Aspose.Email for Python via .NET but they are implemented in Aspose.Email for .NET: Microsoft Graph REST API Exchange API New Enhancements Aspose.Email for Python via .NET staritng version 22.9 has an experimental support of MacOS platform.
